div(layout='row' layout-align='center center')
    md-content(flex='50' layout-padding)
        //- TITLE
        md-card-title
          md-card-title-text
            span.md-headline Nuevo tipo de activo
            p.md-body-1
              | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit.
              | Ipsa ducimus quas alias iusto, voluptas esse, aspernatur nobis
              | reprehenderit! Provident, error eaque veniam maxime optio in
              | dolorem sequi quaerat voluptate quae.
        md-content
            md-input-container.md-block(flex='')
                label Tipo de activo
                input(type='text' ng-model='$ctrl.model.tipo')
            md-input-container.md-block(flex='')
                label Descripci√≥n
                textarea(type='text' ng-model='$ctrl.model.descripcion')
            div(ng-repeat='caracteristica in $ctrl.model.caracteristicas')
                md-card()
                    md-card-title
                      md-card-title-text
                        span.md-headline Caracteristica # {{$index+1}}
                    md-card-content(layout='column')
                        md-input-container.md-block(flex)
                            label Caracteristica
                            input(type='text' ng-model='caracteristica.name')
                        md-chips(ng-model='caracteristica.values' placeholder='Valores')
                            md-chip-template
                                strong {{$chip}}
                div(layout='row' ng-if='$last' layout-align='space-between center')
                    md-input-container.md-block( )
                      md-button.md-icon-button.md-primary(
                        aria-label='More3'
                        ng-click='$ctrl.addCaracteristica()')
                        i.material-icons add
                        md-tooltip Agregar caracteristica
                    md-button.md-primary.md-raised(
                    ng-click='$ctrl.addTipo()'
                        type='button',
                        ng-disabled='$ctrl.btnDisabled') Registrar

